-   * Create a AsyncDiskServices with a set of volumes (specified by their
-   * root directories).
-   * 
-   * The AsyncDiskServices uses one ThreadPool per volume to do the async
-   * disk operations.
-   * 
-   * @param localFileSystem The localFileSystem used for deletions.
